flowchart LR
    Client[Client] -->|POST /run| API[src/api/main.py]

    API -->|optional semantic lookup| Chroma[(Chroma video cache)]
    API -->|ainvoke| Graph[src/agent/graph.py]
    API -->|trace callbacks| Langfuse[(Langfuse)]

    Graph --> Analyze[analyze_user_prompt]
    Analyze --> Research[research_router + research_topic]
    Research --> Planner[plan_video]
    Planner --> Retrieval[src/rag retriever]
    Retrieval --> CodeGen[generate_code_outline + generate_code]
    CodeGen --> Executor[src/agent/execute_code.py]

    Executor -->|POST /jobs| Worker[manim-worker/app.py]
    Worker -->|run manim| Manim[Manim renderer]
    Worker -->|upload final mp4| R2[(R2 bucket)]
    Worker -->|local fallback| Published[/published static files]

    Executor -->|poll /jobs/{job_id}| Worker
    Worker -->|job status + video_url| Executor
    Executor --> Graph
    Graph --> API
    API -->|cache successful URL| Chroma
    API -->|JSON result| Client

    Worker -->|worker observations| Langfuse
